<materialsCitation id="3B923C8CFFC2FFACFCFE180EFE0FF3A1" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3801074307" pageId="5" pageNumber="351">“LaJolla, California, 32° 51° 41” N. Lat., 117° 15' 19° W. Long.”</materialsCitation>
